queries.queryString:
_sourceCategory="*qualys*" "assetInventory" {{tagName}} {{ip}} {{hostname}}
| parse regex "tagName\":\"(?<tagName>.*?)\"" multi
| count by tagName
| sort by _count

_sourceCategory="*qualys*" "assetInventory" {{ip}} {{hostname}} {{tagName}}
| parse regex "\"assetUUID\"\:\"(?<assetUUID>[^\"]+)" 
| count as count by assetUUID
| count

_sourceCategory="*qualys*" "assetInventory" {{tagName}} {{ip}} {{hostname}}
| parse regex "score\"\:(?<criticality>\d+)"
| count criticality
| sort by _count

panels.title: Last Logged On User By Host

queries.queryString:
_sourceCategory="*qualys*" "assetInventory" {{tagName}} {{ip}} {{hostname}}
| parse regex "dnsName\"\:\"(?<hostname>[^\"]+)" nodrop
| where !(_size=65536)
| parse regex "lastLoggedOnUser\"\:\"(?<lastLoggedOnUser>[^\"]+)" nodrop
//| where !isNull(lastLoggedOnUser) AND !isEmpty(lastLoggedOnUser)
| count lastLoggedOnUser,hostname
| fields -_count

_sourceCategory="*qualys*" "assetInventory" {{ip}} {{hostname}} {{tagName}}
| parse regex "\"assetUUID\"\:\"(?<assetUUID>[^\"]+)"
| parse regex "\"provider\"\:\"?(?<provider>[^\"\,]+)" nodrop
| parse regex "\"netbiosName\"\:\"?(?<netbiosName>[^\"\,]+)" nodrop
| parse regex "\"domainRole\"\:\"?(?<domainRole>[^\"\,]+)" nodrop
| toUpperCase(provider) as provider
| toUpperCase(netbiosName) as netbiosName
| if((provider="NULL" or isNull(provider) or isEmpty(provider)) and (domainRole matches "*Workstation*" or netbiosName matches "*MACBOOK*" or netbiosName matches "*MBP*"), "Workstation", provider) as provider
| if((isNull(provider) or provider="NULL" or isEmpty(provider)),"Other",provider) as provider
| count by provider, assetUUID
| count by provider
| sort by _count

_sourceCategory="*qualys*" "assetInventory" {{ip}} {{hostname}} {{tagName}}
| parse regex "\"assetUUID\"\:\"(?<assetUUID>[^\"]+)"
| parse regex "\"agent\"\:(?<agentActivation>[^\,]+)"
| where agentActivation="null" and !isNull(assetUUID)
| count as count by assetUUID
| count

panels.title: Hosts w/ Active Modules and No Agent

queries.queryString:
_sourceCategory="*qualys*" "assetInventory" {{ip}} {{hostname}} {{tagName}}
| parse regex "\"assetUUID\"\:\"(?<assetUUID>[^\"]+)"
| parse regex "\"activatedForModules\"\:(?<modules>\[.*?\])"
| parse regex "\"agent\"\:(?<agentActivation>[^\,]+)" nodrop
| where !(modules = "[]") and !(modules = "[ ]") and agentActivation = "null"
| count as count by assetUUID
| count

_sourceCategory="*qualys*" "assetInventory" {{tagName}} {{ip}} {{hostname}}
| parse regex "\"assetUUID\"\:\"(?<assetUUID>[^\"]+)"
| parse regex "\"errorStatus\"\:(?<assetUUID>\w+)"
| where !isNull(errorStatus) and !(errorStatus = "false")
| count as count by assetUUID
| count

panels.text: Inventory Details   (Filter By Tag Name to Return Assets with Only That Tag)

queries.queryString:
_sourceCategory="*qualys*" "assetInventory" {{tagName}} {{ip}} {{hostname}}
| parse regex "\"assetUUID\"\:\"(?<assetUUID>[^\"]+)" 
| parse regex "port\":(?<open_ports>.*?)\," multi
| transactionize assetUUID (merge open_ports join with ",")
| replace(open_ports, ",", "\n") as open_ports
| count open_ports
| fields -_count

_sourceCategory="*qualys*" "assetInventory" {{tagName}} {{ip}} {{hostname}}
| parse regex "\"softwareListData\"\:\[(?<soft_list>.*?)\]"
| replace(soft_list, ",", "\n") as soft_list
| replace(soft_list, "\"", "") as software_list
| count software_list
| fields -_count

_sourceCategory="*qualys*" "assetInventory" {{tagName}} {{ip}} {{hostname}}
| json field=_raw "operatingSystem.osName" as OS
| json field=_raw "hardware.productName" as productName
| json field=_raw "hardware.manufacturer" as manufacturer
| json field=_raw "hardware.category" as category
| json field=_raw "hardware.fullName" as fullName
| count by fullName, productName, manufacturer, OS, category
| fields -_count

_sourceCategory="*qualys*" "assetInventory" {{tagName}} {{ip}} {{hostname}}
| parse regex "\"assetUUID\"\:\"(?<assetUUID>[^\"]+)" 
| json field=_raw "serviceList.service" as service_list
| parse regex field=service_list "description\"\:.*?\,\"name\"\:\"(?<service_name>.*?)\"\,\"status\"\:\"(?<status>.*?)\"\}" multi
| concat(service_name, "\t-\t", "Status: ", status) as service_status
| transactionize assetUUID (merge service_status join with "\n")
| count by service_status
| fields -_count
